wstunnel bundled binaries
=============================

This directory ships the pre-built wstunnel release tarballs that
phantom_frontmatter extracts at `setup init` time. The linux/amd64
and linux/arm64 archives below are produced by the ARAS-Workspace
fork's "Release Linux" workflow and dropped here verbatim.

References:

  ARAS-Workspace/wstunnel (fork)             - https://github.com/ARAS-Workspace/wstunnel
  erebe/wstunnel (upstream)                  - https://github.com/erebe/wstunnel
  v10.5.2 release (source of these tarballs) - https://github.com/ARAS-Workspace/wstunnel/releases/tag/v10.5.2
  Build run that produced v10.5.2 archives   - https://github.com/ARAS-Workspace/wstunnel/actions/runs/24295740708
  main branch commit history                 - https://github.com/ARAS-Workspace/wstunnel/commits/main/

Files in this directory:

  wstunnel_<VERSION>_linux_amd64.tar.gz - bundled amd64 tarball (extracted at setup init)
  wstunnel_<VERSION>_linux_arm64.tar.gz - bundled arm64 tarball (extracted at setup init)
  checksums.txt                         - sha256sums emitted by the release workflow
